# We Dispatch!, We Pickup!!, and We Dropoff!!!. Welcome to TaxiSim.

## MVP
<ul>
<li>- [x] Window View Patches (street top-view)</li>
<li>- [x] Spawn Cars (randomly on street)</li>
<li>- [x] Randomly Generate Rides (pick and dropoff location)</li>
<li>- [x] Dispatch Taxi (nearest taxi to the pickup location)</li>
<li>- [x] Driving Taxi (heads to the pickup location then to the dropoff location) </li>
</ul>

